          <title>Samsung Debuts Galaxy Tab S10 FE and S10 FE Plus: Larger Screens, Lower Prices</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Samsung has launched two new tablets, the Galaxy Tab S10 FE and S10 FE Plus, featuring larger screens and lower prices. The latter model boasts a 13.1-inch display, while both devices offer improved AI features, glare-reducing Vision Booster technology, and support for the S Pen stylus.]]></description>
